      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Common questions</h2>
        <p class="sub">Quick answers to help you get started.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq">
        <details>
          <summary>Do colleges really accept CLEP credits?</summary>
          <div>Thousands of accredited colleges accept CLEP. Always check your target school’s CLEP policy.</div>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Is CLEP only for “top students”?</summary>
          <div>No. With focused prep and practice, most motivated students can pass and earn credit.</div>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>How much can I save?</summary>
          <div>Many exams award ~3 credits. At typical tuition rates, that can exceed $1,500 per exam.</div>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Which apps are free vs. paid?</summary>
          <div>Five iOS apps are free (US History I, US History II, Principles of Marketing, Natural Sciences, Humanities). Biology is a premium app.</div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

